    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The exterior retains a healthy shine with only minor, age-appropriate blemishes like small stone chips on the hood. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing light wear on the driver's seat bolster but no tears or unpleasant odors. Mechanically, the car is sound, having undergone regular servicing to ensure it drives smoothly and reliably for many miles to come.",
